{"title":"The Best Laptop","clock":false,"countdown":0,"intro":{"buttons":{"start":"Start"},"content":[]},"activity":{"scenes":[{"block":"scene","name":"SC1","countdown":0,"instructions":{"open":true,"content":[{"block":"group","class":"flex gap-2 items-center","content":[{"block":"audio","class":"","file":"files/A2-2U5L5EA-INS.mp3","wave":false,"autoplay":false,"id":"","name":"vany"},{"block":"text","class":"","text":"Read and listen to a conversation between a teacher and his student talking about buying a new laptop.","id":"","name":"PXQP"}]}]},"content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-3 my-2 max-w-5xl mx-auto","content":[{"marker":"","class":"bg-yellow-700 p-2 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"flex justify-center mask mask-squircle bg-orange-500 p-2 my-10","content":[{"file":"files/A2-2U5L5EA-IMG-01.jpg","class":"w-2/4 mask mask-squircle","id":"v2sY","block":"image","name":"myHN"}],"background":"","id":"mlW0vmHT","block":"group","name":"4LiF","hidden":false},{"marker":"","class":"bg-orange-500 p-2 my-10 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"bg-slate-50 rounded.lg p-5","content":[{"file":"files/A2-2U5L5EA-Listening_mezcla.mp3","wave":true,"class":"","autoplay":false,"id":"rOFc","block":"audio","name":"AqAv"}],"background":"","id":"2HNE","block":"group","name":"prTb"}],"background":"","id":"IAn189tV","block":"group","name":"rNKq","hidden":false},{"marker":"","class":"bg-orange-500 p-2 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"text-xl p-10 text-2xl bg-slate-50 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ","content":[{"text":"Are you looking for the best smartspeaker on the market? Look no further than that the SuperAlixa X, the latest and greatest gadget from Nozama. This speaker has all you need and more, with features that will exceed your expectations. Here are some of the characteristics why the SuperAlixa X is the ultimate smartspeaker:","class":"","id":"nxtxvbWu","block":"text","name":"jiTX","hidden":true}],"background":"","id":"7d2Xc060","block":"group","name":"1GBV"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"fluent-emoji-flat:man-teacher-medium","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J9Mt9a","block":"icon","name":"Qf7p"},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"Hi, I heard you are looking for a new laptop for your homework. Do you have any idea what kind of laptop you want?","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiAYoH6","block":"text","name":"VNuZ"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNlKzJ","block":"group","name":"m4as"}],"background":"","id":"dWSjswQR3Tl2","block":"group","name":"Yoes"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"noto-v1:man-student-medium-light-skin-tone","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J926agGLSz","block":"icon","name":"zrMn"},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"Well, I want the fastest, the most reliable and obviously the most affordable possible. But there are so many options out there, I don't know which one is the best.","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4GfKus","block":"text","name":"PLEE"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFoapf","block":"group","name":"iRhW"}],"background":"","id":"qBGgUnycXq02","block":"group","name":"28hm"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"fluent-emoji-flat:man-teacher-medium","class":"text-5xl ","id":"45J926ag9gsOAfsF","block":"icon","name":"eq1C","hidden":false},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"Ok, I understand. It can be overwhelming to choose from so many brands and models. But don't worry, I can help you narrow down your choices. What do you use your laptop for mostly?","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4G8lRUbZ6t","block":"text","name":"y5Ft"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFsUgtTRpB","block":"group","name":"Qro8"}],"background":"","id":"7V3rWJdINIZx","block":"group","name":"yINr"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"noto-v1:man-student-medium-light-skin-tone","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J926ag9gsOMFJKonb3","block":"icon","name":"w48z","hidden":false},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"I use it for writing essays, doing research, watching videos and playing some games.","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4G8lRUdDTe5BNI","block":"text","name":"jtVz"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFsUgt9q8UqxlS","block":"group","name":"H2Gx"}],"background":"","id":"HijidOBWrA3t","block":"group","name":"UG5g"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"fluent-emoji-flat:man-teacher-medium","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J926ag9gsOMFJKsu0qa4Lq","block":"icon","name":"taiV"},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"OK, then you need a laptop that has the most reliable processor, not the biggest memory and storage only a decent amount is perfect, and a nice screen. You don't need the most powerful graphics card or the largest battery if you are not gaming or working for long hours without plugging in. Do you?","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4G8lRUdDTenrOgyRcK","block":"text","name":"ziMk"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFsUgt9q8UERk8bsbk","block":"group","name":"j1Zy"}],"background":"","id":"80ABs9wf2kbl","block":"group","name":"OvVc"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"noto-v1:man-student-medium-light-skin-tone","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J926ag9gsOMFJKsu0qZfZ5L6P3","block":"icon","name":"pYR5"},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"No, I don’t. Do you have any recommendations for me?","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4G8lRUdDTenrOgmwFBebh1","block":"text","name":"3Xxb"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFsUgt9q8UERk8N2TAZbxe","block":"group","name":"O5ku"}],"background":"","id":"9URyBpwMETNA","block":"group","name":"4pXi"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"fluent-emoji-flat:man-teacher-medium","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J926ag9gsOMFJKsu0qZfZ5L6P3h0xV","block":"icon","name":"pp66"},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"Sure. I think the best option for you is the Kenovo Notebook X. It has the most reliable processor, 8 GB of RAM, 500 GB in the hard drive and a 15-inch full HD display. It is also the lightest and thinnest device, so you can easily carry it around. It’s the most portable one and the best thing it costs only $599, which is the greatest deal for such a high-quality laptop. The internal speakers have the highest quality and the keyboard is the coolest I have seen. You can connect it with all the printers through wi-fi. ","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4G8lRUdDTenrOgmwFBebh1XeHN","block":"text","name":"gwrT"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFsUgt9q8UERk8N2TAZbxeHeHg","block":"group","name":"HOf5"}],"background":"","id":"IFif4V8Q","block":"group","name":"pBeS"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"noto-v1:man-student-medium-light-skin-tone","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J926ag9gsOMFJKsu0qZfZ5L6P3h0xVPBI9","block":"icon","name":"Afng"},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"Wow, that sounds amazing! Thank you so much for your help, teacher. You are the best!","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4G8lRUdDTenrOgmwFBebh1XeHNO818","block":"text","name":"9rTP"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFsUgt9q8UERk8N2TAZbxeHeHgQgGI","block":"group","name":"oCX3"}],"background":"","id":"82x04eoy","block":"group","name":"Gy2y"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5 ml-10 flex ","content":[{"icon":"fluent-emoji-flat:man-teacher-medium","class":"text-5xl","id":"45J926ag9gsOMFJKsu0qZfZ5L6P3h0xVPBI9lKeQ","block":"icon","name":"XwCK"},{"marker":"","class":"ml-10 ","content":[{"text":"You're very welcome, student. I'm glad I could help you find the perfect laptop for your needs. Now go and buy your new laptop!","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA6e4G8lRUdDTenrOgmwFBebh1XeHNO818fAK3","block":"text","name":"WLiM"}],"background":"","id":"EvKNEOaFsUgt9q8UERk8N2TAZbxeHeHgQgGIWQI3","block":"group","name":"XtYa"}],"background":"","id":"Ir4QFr49","block":"group","name":"VyfF"},{"marker":"","class":"my-5","content":[{"text":"The SuperAlixa X is the gadget of your dreams, and it can be yours for only $299. Don’t miss this opportunity to get the best smartspeaker ever made. Order yours today!","class":"","id":"nxtx0SiA4vzYB39C","block":"text","name":"DCzm"}],"background":"","id":"LbafG84zZlAT","block":"group","name":"GVJs","hidden":true}],"background":"","id":"SSOM5ZRV","block":"group","name":"MlXj"}],"background":"","id":"ZEBEmlpC","block":"group","name":"pDA6","hidden":false}],"background":"","id":"r3QVbb9L","block":"group","name":"ZDf2","hidden":false}],"background":"","id":"LYwaaEsm","block":"group","name":"G5xA","hidden":false}],"background":"","name":"4Cs6","hidden":false,"marker":"","id":""},{"symbol":"FinalizeGroup"}],"id":""}]},"end":{"buttons":{"restart":false},"content":[{"symbol":"finishedAll"}]},"symbols":{"finishedAll":{"class":"w-full","content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-5 text-center w-full","content":[{"block":"text","text":"Congratulations, you finished the activity.","class":"","name":"Congra"}],"background":"","name":"CongraGroup"},{"block":"group","class":"text-center p-5","content":[{"block":"finished","name":"finishedBlock"}],"background":"","name":"finishedGroup"}],"background":"","block":"group"},"FinalizeGroup":{"block":"group","class":"text-center mt-10","content":[{"block":"button","class":"mx-auto","to":"/end","text":"Finalize","name":"FinalizeBTN"}],"background":""}}}